# Tag

`TxTag` renders a compact status-style label with optional icon, custom color tokens, removable close affordance, and click events for lightweight state toggles.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/tag/src/types.ts`, `TxTag.vue`, and `tag.test.ts`.

